title: Dak Prescott, Tom Brady, Kevin Durant, & NBA rankings
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Tom Brady, Kevin Durant, & NBA rankings
description:
Filling in for Colin, Doug Gottlieb explains why Dak Prescott is asking for too much money, a possible sign Tom Brady might be giving us, more drama surrounding Kevin Durant, and his top teams in the NBA. Guests include James Robinson, BJ Armstrong, Tyrell Williams, and T. J. Houshmandzadeh.
